entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: The population of tempest rills around Mos Eisley has been eradicated.
entries.journal_entry_description: Entha is impressed with your rill killing ability, so impressed that she wants you to do more. In particular she wants some tempest rills killed. Like the other rills, they can be found outside of the city.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Entha is impressed with your work and now wants you to kill 10 of the fierce tempest rills. They can be found outside of the city in the infested areas in the nearby foothills.
entries.task02_comm_message_text: Looks like you have gotten the threat cleared out. Well done. Now, I just need some Rock Mite egg sacks.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Try looking here for some Tempest Rills.
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: Try looking here for some Tempest Rills.
